cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.Medical Imaging, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper presents a method for automatic segmentation of the levator hiatus in ultrasound images using a convolutional neural network (CNN) with a novel activation function. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the application of the method is in medical imaging (cs.Medical Imaging) and the use of the novel activation function is a topic of interest in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
